For those that are scared shitless by Raging Brachy, I only remind you that in MHW we have something that in Ultimate 4 you don't: the slinger.
Hit the slimed parts with it and you neutralize most of the explosive danger. Stagger the moster with it. Use the water slinger ammo to cleanse the slime off of it.
It's all about using all of the stuff you have available.
